`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Heal
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Syntax: 

 * cast 'heal' <character>

 This is the application of the caster's Will upon the wounds of the target.
Higher level spells, which use more Will, can heal greater wounds. 

 (see 'help Healer' for details on the heal command)

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
